{"tid":1639963,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［同我每人讀一千次］唔係被拘捕，黑警無權帶你走","createTime":"2019-10-08T19:42:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T17:07:39.000Z","uid":207814,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e2b87f592ede07099d2fe3f98a9b02f080dd0101","tid":1639963,"uid":207814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T19:42:00.000Z","msg":"利申：前執法人員，但唔係前狗。<br />\n<br />\n尋日見到呢個post,想分享下作為被黑警stop and search既學生、幫口既路人，其實可以有乜權利。<br />\n<br />\n金鐘尋日黑警<br />\n黨鐵黑警見戴口罩學生即捉 捉埋幫口嘅路人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1638918\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1638918</a><br />\n<br />\n1）先分析警權：stop &amp; Search - Section 54 Cap232<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hklii.org/chi/hk/legis/ord/232/s54.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hklii.org%2Fchi%2Fhk%2Flegis%2Ford%2F232%2Fs54.html&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6VuQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=43c231cc\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hklii.org/chi/hk/legis/ord/232/s54.html</a><br />\n<br />\n黑警如果發現有人&ldquo;行動可疑&rdquo;，係可以截停、查身份證、扣留可疑人一段合理期間（即係查證、搜身其間唔可以走開，但查完無拘捕行動就要放走）<br />\n<br />\n至於乜嘢叫做&rdquo;行動可疑&rdquo;，老實講呢個係黑警既主觀判斷，無得爭拗。<br />\n<br />\n拒絕以上黑警要求，有機會觸犯&ldquo;阻差辦公&rdquo; Section 63 Cap232<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hklii.org/chi/hk/legis/ord/232/s63.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hklii.org%2Fchi%2Fhk%2Flegis%2Ford%2F232%2Fs63.html&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6VuQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=21beb8fe\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hklii.org/chi/hk/legis/ord/232/s63.html</a><br />\n<br />\n至於被搜查人士，係可以拒絕異性搜身或者要求去警署進行搜身，但邊有人無啦啦會要求入警署先？<br />\n<br />\n2. 呢件事上學生同埋屌狗既路人係畀黑警帶左去黨鐵職員房。但留意返point 1，警察喺無拘捕既情形下係無權利帶走一個市民。所以學生同埋路人最後入左黨鐵職員房，係有以下兩個可能性：<br />\na)已經被拘捕（但我哋睇極都唔明學生同幫口路人犯左乜嘢法）<br />\nb)學生同路人當時係自願跟黑警入去黨鐵職員房<br />\n<br />\n3)所以，作為被stop &amp; search既人士，如果警察要帶你走，記住要問清楚黑警你係咪已經被拘捕。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔係被拘捕，黑警無權帶你走，你只係需要on the spot協助黑警完成查身份證同搜身，完成就走得。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n如果係拘捕，要問清楚佢拘捕你係乜嘢罪名。<br />\n正常情況下，警拘捕後係會即時向你警戒(即係講&rdquo;除非出於自願，你可以唔講嘢&rdquo;嗰抽句子）拘捕後任何情況都&ldquo;我無嘢講&rdquo;應該唔駛我教。"},{"pid":"666757c9a390cc9423030bc0f9917959c35d4b32","tid":1639963,"uid":227271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T19:49:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e32516a31c00867bf742ba50ab4391cd66a25e1a","tid":1639963,"uid":126366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T19:50:47.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a4b3e07bda1815aaca905b11ed5728d7320a13f5","tid":1639963,"uid":22018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T19:55:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fcb552ed635803b636f94b9e075ef18a62c59c3b","tid":1639963,"uid":207122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T19:58:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf2f083629b4099d3b357c50c95a9adb31c3074f","tid":1639963,"uid":329742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T20:14:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a398085679324a9caae4e130fd4e73ba78e8153a","tid":1639963,"uid":321079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e2b87f592ede07099d2fe3f98a9b02f080dd0101","tid":1639963,"uid":207814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T19:42:00.000Z","msg":"利申：前執法人員，但唔係前狗。<br />\n<br />\n尋日見到呢個post,想分享下作為被黑警stop and search既學生、幫口既路人，其實可以有乜權利。<br />\n<br />\n金鐘尋日黑警<br />\n黨鐵黑警見戴口罩學生即捉 捉埋幫口嘅路人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1638918\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1638918</a><br />\n<br />\n1）先分析警權：stop &amp; Search - Section 54 Cap232<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hklii.org/chi/hk/legis/ord/232/s54.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hklii.org%2Fchi%2Fhk%2Flegis%2Ford%2F232%2Fs54.html&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6VuQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=43c231cc\" target=\