ime":"2019-10-09T11:55:51.000Z","msg":"如果佢老屈我是但一條罪 咁我應該點？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T16:30:03.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講，full stop."},{"pid":"7cc3055cf48634365c3252265c3f4d8c0a441622","tid":1639963,"uid":143321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4c65e02b6e8da111216fb2b372b5b31b0c81b80","tid":1639963,"uid":207814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"89041dde5013e04001bc82707354cfb100a990b3","tid":1639963,"uid":203602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:55:51.000Z","msg":"如果佢老屈我是但一條罪 咁我應該點？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T16:30:03.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講，full stop."},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T16:48:15.000Z","msg":"如果佢唔出委任證，但要查身分證，可唔可以拒絕？<br />\n如果咁樣俾佢帶返警署，算唔算已經被拘捕？"},{"pid":"a79c61956d6dd737dafdf5f6486d0f6dd24e9796","tid":1639963,"uid":143321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7cc3055cf48634365c3252265c3f4d8c0a441622","tid":1639963,"uid":143321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4c65e02b6e8da111216fb2b372b5b31b0c81b80","tid":1639963,"uid":207814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"89041dde5013e04001bc82707354cfb100a990b3","tid":1639963,"uid":203602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:55:51.000Z","msg":"如果佢老屈我是但一條罪 咁我應該點？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T16:30:03.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講，full stop."},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T16:48:15.000Z","msg":"如果佢唔出委任證，但要查身分證，可唔可以拒絕？<br />\n如果咁樣俾佢帶返警署，算唔算已經被拘捕？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T16:52:09.000Z","msg":"例如：俾佢9 告行為不檢"},{"pid":"d05a9369be44a5d8497fd2dab9661acb0bef5e61","tid":1639963,"uid":207814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7cc3055cf48634365c3252265c3f4d8c0a441622","tid":1639963,"uid":143321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4c65e02b6e8da111216fb2b372b5b31b0c81b80","tid":1639963,"uid":207814,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"89041dde5013e04001bc82707354cfb100a990b3","tid":1639963,"uid":203602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T11:55:51.000Z","msg":"如果佢老屈我是但一條罪 咁我應該點？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T16:30:03.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講，full stop."},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T16:48:15.000Z","msg":"如果佢唔出委任證，但要查身分證，可唔可以拒絕？<br />\n如果咁樣俾佢帶返警署，算唔算已經被拘捕？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T17:07:39.000Z","msg":"無軍裝在場得便衣既話，有人話自己係popo要查你嘢，你點都要保護自己要求佢地至少一位（所謂行駛警權嗰位）出示委任證。<br />\n<br />\n其他情況，就睇你有無時間有無guts去玩。你可以要求軍裝、便衣show warrant card，但以而家佢哋既氣燄，你唔同佢地行個軍禮鞠個90度躬仲要攞warrant card？帶你返警署你咪唔駛懷疑佢身份囉。"}]}